# SQL.txt Documentation

## When to Update

- **On feature completion** — Update Getting Started, API docs, CLI reference, feature docs
- **On API change** — Update XML comments and generated docs
- **On CLI change** — Update docs/cli-reference.md and examples

## Required Content

- **Getting Started** — Prerequisites, build, minimal example, next steps
- **Public API** — XML docs for all public types/members (purpose, params, returns, exceptions)
- **CLI Reference** — Command syntax, options, examples, exit codes
- **Feature docs** — Per-feature sections with usage of related features

## Locations

- docs/getting-started.md
- docs/cli-reference.md
- docs/architecture/05-documentation-standards.md
- docs/samples/wiki-database.md
